data.description:
The Nevada is a super two-story home with an open living area. As you walk into the home, you step into a foyer that leads into a large great room open to kitchen and dining room. Super kitchen with large island, granite countertops, and tile backsplash. Beautiful wood cabinets with crown molding. Stainless steel appliances and large walk-in pantry. Three wonderful bedrooms upstairs with two baths upstairs and a powder room downstairs. The Primary bedroom has a walk-in closet, on suite with double vanity and separate shower. Ceramic tile throughout the living areas and bath, carpet in bedrooms stairs and upstairs walkway. All this plus central refrigerated air. and shutters on major windows
Photos are for demonstration purposes only and not of actual home - Home is Under Construction.
